query: SELECT MIN(chn.name) AS voiced_char, MIN(n.name) AS voicing_actress, MIN(t.title) AS voiced_animation FROM aka_name AS an, complete_cast AS cc, comp_cast_type AS cct1, comp_cast_type AS cct2, char_name AS chn, cast_info AS ci, company_name AS cn, info_type AS it, info_type AS it3, keyword AS k, movie_companies AS mc, movie_info AS mi, movie_keyword AS mk, name AS n, person_info AS pi, role_type AS rt, title AS t WHERE t.id = mi.movie_id AND t.id = mc.movie_id AND t.id = ci.movie_id AND t.id = mk.movie_id AND t.id = cc.movie_id AND mc.movie_id = ci.movie_id AND mc.movie_id = mi.movie_id AND mc.movie_id = mk.movie_id AND mc.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = ci.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = mk.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = mk.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND mk.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND cn.id = mc.company_id AND it.id = mi.info_type_id AND n.id = ci.person_id AND rt.id = ci.role_id AND n.id = an.person_id AND ci.person_id = an.person_id AND chn.id = ci.person_role_id AND n.id = pi.person_id AND ci.person_id = pi.person_id AND it3.id = pi.info_type_id AND k.id = mk.keyword_id AND cct1.id = cc.subject_id AND cct2.id = cc.status_id AND t.production_year > 2008 AND (t.title like '%train%') AND (n.name like '%g%' OR n.name like '%b%') AND (k.keyword like '%rebellion%') AND cct2.kind not in ('complete','complete+verified') AND (chn.name like '%Don Corleone%') AND it3.info in ('novel','essays','soundtrack','magazine cover photo','LD certification','LD disc format','weekend gross','birth name','LD subtitles','LD frequency response','votes distribution','trivia','adaption','LD year','LD video standard','LD analog right','release dates','LD quality of source','biographical movies','production process protocol') AND it.info not in ('LD color rendition','LD picture format','color info','LD master format','LD audio noise','salary history','trade mark','keywords','magazine cover photo','LD category','LD analog left','LD disc format','languages','weekend gross','LD number of sides') AND (cn.name like '%A24%' OR cn.name like '%Lionsgate%' OR cn.name like '%Working Title Films%') AND cn.country_code in ('pt','cu','sd','lk','et') AND mi.info in ('Macedonian','Welsh','Portuguese','Afrikaans','Brazilian Sign Language') AND mc.note not like '%Italy%' AND mc.note not like '%Germany%'
